label: Hermetschwil, Benediktinerinnenkloster, Cod. chart. 140

metadata.label: Summary (English)
metadata.value: This book of hours contains primarily the Office of the Dead and the Office of the Virgin. The initials are clearly set off from one another by color and enliven the text.
